videos.headline: Southeast Missouri State bench amped up after 3-pointer
videos.description: Dylan Branson drains a corner 3-pointer for Southeast Missouri State, and the bench is loving it.

tracking.trackingName: *UNPUB 6/30* NCB_One-Play (Southeast Missouri State bench amped up after 3-pointer) 2023/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chris Harris gets a friendly bounce for Southeast Missouri State
videos.description: Southeast Missouri State's Chris Harris puts up a short jumper that bounces off the rim and in.

tracking.trackingName: *UNPUB 6/30* NCB_One-Play (Chris Harris gets a friendly bounce for Southeast Missouri State) 2022/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trevian Tennyson speeds in for a Texas A&M-Corpus Christi and-1
videos.description: Texas A&M-Corpus Christi's Trevian Tennyson gets to the rim in transition for a tough and-1.

tracking.trackingName: *UNPUB 6/30* NCB_One-Play (Trevian Tennyson speeds in for a Texas A&M-Corpus Christi and-1) 2022/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trevian Tennyson drops tough scoop layup
videos.description: Trevian Tennyson gets to the rack for a tough scoop layup to extend Texas A&M-Corpus Christi's lead.

tracking.trackingName: *UNPUB 6/30* NCB_One-Play (Trevian Tennyson drops tough scoop layup) 2022/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas A&M-Corpus Christi earns first NCAA tournament win
videos.description: The Texas A&M-Corpus Christi Islanders hold off the Southeast Missouri State Redhawks and advance to face No. 1 seed Alabama.
